title: 073: Supplement Regulation, Personal Accomplishments & Party Animals
description: PumpHead questions, we love 'em! In this episode Sal, Adam and Justin answer your questions about whether supplements should be regulated, their biggest fitness/personal accomplishments and how to stay on track with your fitness goals when your friends are party animals.
